{"product_id":"nurme-lavender-shampoo-pro-vit-b5-250ml","title":"NURME Lavender Shampoo ProVitamin B5 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNurme’s natural shampoos are based on raw materials recognized by eco-certifications. The shampoo contains only plant-based ingredients. It is gentle for your hair and for the environment.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNurme Lavender Shampoo helps to repair damaged hair and split ends while promoting hair growth. In addition, the enchanting scent of lavender has a soothing effect.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo contains gentle surfactants that create a creamy lather and are mild on the skin. The hair-strengthening ProVitamin B5 helps reduce hair damage and split ends.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLavender essential oil is richly nourishing, moisturizes the scalp and hair, helps prevent hair loss, and improves scalp circulation, thereby promoting hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse the shampoo together with lavender hair conditioner to make your hair silky, easy to comb, and shiny from roots to ends.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-Glucoside**, Sodium Coco-Sulfate**, Sodium Chloride**, Panthenol (ProVitamin B5), Citric Acid**, Glyceryl Oleate**, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein**, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Oil, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate**, Linalool*. *Occures naturally in essential oils. **Natural cosmetics approved ingredient, organic.\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% Parabens | 0% Silicones | 0% Synthetic and fragrances\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553853612359,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-lavender-shampoo-provitamin-b5-250ml-378356.jpg?v=1739897244","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-lavender-shampoo-pro-vit-b5-250ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}